MODULE ComplexModule
  IMPLICIT NONE
  TYPE :: ComplexType
     REAL :: real, imag
  CONTAINS
     OPERATOR(+) (a, b) RESULT(c)
       TYPE(ComplexType), INTENT(IN) :: a, b
       TYPE(ComplexType) :: c
       c%real = a%real + b%real
       c%imag = a%imag + b%imag
     END OPERATOR
  END TYPE ComplexType
END MODULE ComplexModule
